platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: An intriguing genre blend, Terraria mixes collection, construction, and combat in a retro-styled 2D adventure. Break apart the world, uncovering rare treasures and digging deep underground for resources to build elaborate houses. Then craft powerful weapons and armor before facing bizarre, fantastical creatures. Its a huge, sophisticated experience thats easy to spend hours witha universe of densely layered surprises, where every session is exciting.
